Basically bottomfeeding from FN but

Europe - Group A

A B C.

Point System: 3 Points for a #1 Victory 1 Point For a Revival (?) 1 Point For a Kill(edited)

Mark 24-Feb-20 12:58 PM
OKAY so to summarize it all up (for people who don't want to scroll up) Spring Cup would be hosted through arena mode. It starts on a weekend, arena mode is open from 12PM EST to like 6PM EST (so all timezones can play, even aussies.) Arena mode would be closed throughout the week and only open on Saturday and Sunday. Each player gets a total of 10 games- they can play 5 on Saturday and 5 on Sunday, or play all of them on Saturday, or play all of them on Sunday. There's a leaderboard ingame, and like the top 30 qualify for semi finals. Then we get that down to 15 once semi finals, and then we send the top 15 over to finals...or something like that. Basically, it's something like how FN operates their tournaments.
